<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to {{appName}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #560c32, #f7a50c);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 20px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .tagline {
            font-size: 14px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .welcome-icon {
            font-size: 64px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .title {
            font-size: 32px;
            color: #2b303a;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .subtitle {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f7a50c, #e6940b);
            color: white;
            padding: 18px 40px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 25px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(247, 165, 12, 0.3);
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(247, 165, 12, 0.4);
        }
        .features {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        .features h3 {
            color: #2b303a;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .feature-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .feature-list li {
            padding: 8px 0;
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 25px;
        }
        .feature-list li:before {
            content: '‚ú®';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #410125;
            color: #95979c;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 25px;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .social-links {
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .social-links a {
            color: #95979c;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">{{appName}}</div>
            <div class="tagline">Capture Your Moments</div>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <div class="welcome-icon">üéâ</div>
            <h1 class="title">Welcome, {{userName}}!</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">You're all set to start your journey with {{appName}}</p>
            
            <div class="message">
                <p>Thank you for joining our community! We're thrilled to have you on board. {{appName}} is designed to help you capture, share, and cherish your most precious moments.</p>
                
                <p>Here's what you can do to get started:</p>
            </div>

            <div class="features">
                <h3>What's Next?</h3>
                <ul class="feature-list">
                    <li>Complete your profile to personalize your experience</li>
                    <li>Upload your first moment and share it with friends</li>
                    <li>Explore trending moments from our community</li>
                    <li>Connect with friends and family</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            {{#if buttonUrl}}
            <a href="{{buttonUrl}}" class="cta-button">{{buttonText}}</a>
            {{/if}}

            <p class="message">
                If you have any questions, our support team is here to help. Just reach out to us anytime!
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>{{appName}}</p>
            <p>¬©Ô∏è {{year}} {{companyName}}</p>
            {{#if helpUrl}}
            <p><a href="{{helpUrl}}">Need Help? Contact Support</a></p>
            {{/if}}
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="#">Facebook</a> | 
                <a href="#">Twitter</a> | 
                <a href="#">Instagram</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 